-- MOVES-Northwest Bancshares names William Harvey CFO
-- 
-- Fri Aug 22, 2014 10:09AM EDT
-- None



Aug 22 (Reuters) - Northwest Bancshares Inc <NWBI.O>, the holding company of Northwest Savings Bank, said it appointed William Harvey Jr as its chief financial officer.

The company also named Steven Fisher as chief revenue officer. [ID:nPnbGhlNR] Harvey will be in charge of the bank's technology, operations, finance and support divisions and Fisher will head the production and revenue divisions.